# Ujwala — Personal Portfolio Website

A simple and responsive personal portfolio website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It includes light/dark mode, floating icon animations, and a working contact form powered by EmailJS.

---

## Features
- Responsive design for all devices  
- Light and dark mode toggle  
- Animated floating icons  
- Contact form with EmailJS integration  
- Smooth scrolling and hover effects  

---

## Technologies Used
- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)  
- Font Awesome (Icons)  
- EmailJS (Contact form)  

---

